title: UFYB 129: A Year of Thought Work Vol. 1 - Parenting, Body Image, & COVID-19
itunes:title: A Year of Thought Work Vol. 1 - Parenting, Body Image, & COVID-19
description:
Join us on the podcast this week as The Clutch members, Bessie and Elizabeth, share their lessons learned and the best thought work they’ve done to transform their lives. I’m so excited for them to show you what’s truly possible when you learn how to manage your mind and I know that they’ll inspire you to do the same.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfuckyourbrain.com/129
